727714f-b.title: Queens: Queens Boulevard - Jackson Avenue
727714f-b.text:
9ueens Boulevard, at Jackson Avenue, showing the maze
of elevated structures of the I.R.T. and B.M.T. subway
aystems on the former. The clock tower of the Bank of Man-
hattan Building can be seen in view 1. View 2 shows Krohn's
diner on Jackson Avenue (S.W. corner) and the clock tower of
the Brewster Building, and the nine-story building of the
Queens Light and Power Company.
P. L. Sperr  December 29, 1936
NO REPRODUCTIONS  Views 1,2
